review_blob: Dear God, this beer is awful.  Tried it on draft at Bier-Thirty in Boise ID.  The pumpkin pie spice notes are over the top.  Way too much nutmeg or something similar.  I like a lot of SRB brews, but this one should never have left the brewery.
beer_name: Salmon River One Eyed Pumpkin People Eater

review_blob: Tasted on tap.  A distinctly nutty aroma with almond/hazelnut prevalent.  Taste very balanced, with nutty malt and lightly citrus hop notes.  Though this beer has a sweet aroma, it doesnt taste sweet.  A very well done brown ale.
